Text: New Procedures for Enron IT PurchasingStarting Enron IT Purchasing will no longer be able to receive orders for IT equipment To place an order please proceed to the following website insert link Any orders sent to Enron IT Purchasing before this date will be processed you do not need to enter another request Enron IT Purchasing will still be open to status requests approval notifications and pricing inquiries Thank you very much for your patience and cooperation IT Sourcing and Procurement
